item.description: We are devoted to fashion that speaks of quality, attention to detail and timeless elegance. We like to represent the movement against the wear-and-tear-culture that has been prolific ever since the entrance of the large market chains. That's why we only pick and shop high quality garments for our clients and why all our editorials and commercial work we do only showcases some of the very best contemporary fashion designed and manufactured in Europe.
